        "title": "End of Beginning",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Act 1:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "An event or a situation brings the Protagonists together and forces them to spend time cooperating to achieve a goal. This event raises the tension and stakes and allows for a clear definition of each of the Protagonist's goals. While still at odds with each other, sparks are starting to fly. In Romance stories, attention must be paid to the External (outside forces that impact the relationship) and Internal Relationship Arcs (beliefs, decisions, and actions of the Protagonists that impact the relationship). "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "External: What event forces the Protagonists to spend time together? (e.g. snowstorm, disaster cleanup, work project, or competition.)"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Internal: What action or choice do the characters make that reflects their desire for each other? (e.g. defending each other, being extra helpful, or thoughtful action.)"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Remember, sparks are beginning to fly, but the Protagonists are still in a state of denial."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 1 makes up the first 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "End of Beginning should occur at around the 25% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
