            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Act 3:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Protagonists are now together and moving into their happily ever after that readers have been waiting for. They are now fully committed and perfect for each other, with new perspectives in life. (Unless it is a happily ever... for now.)"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Show how the Protagonists have changed over the course of the story and how they now interact with each other and their ordinary world. They must be in an opposite state from the beginning."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Allow the Protagonists a moment of enjoyment and celebration â€“ they have earned it."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "If part of a series, consider leaving a hook for the next installment."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 3 makes up the final 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Resolution should occur at around the 99% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
